2017;;All Saints;;American;;Steve Gomer;;Steve Gomer (director); Steve Armour (screenplay); John Corbett, Cara Buono;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/All_Saints_(film);;Based on a true story, a salesman-turned-pastor Michael Spurlock of a tiny Episcopal (Anglican) church in Smyrna, Tennessee is ordered to shut it down. He attempts to save the church, as well as a group of refugees from Karen State, Myanmar in Southeast Asia.